陣，我唔係醫生答你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話成日生飛茲嗰啲就可以食維他命B雜預防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係好少生飛茲<br />\n<br />\n不過唔該同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc0d5656099a79b70813a30362ad312256a051f","tid":387540,"uid":6270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:09:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我試過，好相似<br />\n去睇普通診所<br />\n醫生話係口腔潰瘍（嚴重版飛滋）<br />\n食幾日藥同用漱口水就康復</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲搞到我以為出智慧齒搞到頂住<br />\n聽日去睇睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952e2448aead2734c91cf26fdeadbe0f9cc01a43","tid":387540,"uid":1993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:14:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我試過，好相似<br />\n去睇普通診所<br />\n醫生話係口腔潰瘍（嚴重版飛滋）<br />\n食幾日藥同用漱口水就康復</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲搞到我以為出智慧齒搞到頂住<br />\n聽日去睇睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰時我都以為係智慧齒<br />\n同你一樣生係最入嘅角位<br />\n飲水都痛到仆街<br />\n快啲睇，我知係好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ce6613e0448e7f09fa7abb7c42a1c1f42a47da","tid":387540,"uid":6270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:18:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我試過，好相似<br />\n去睇普通診所<br />\n醫生話係口腔潰瘍（嚴重版飛滋）<br />\n食幾日藥同用漱口水就康復</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲搞到我以為出智慧齒搞到頂住<br />\n聽日去睇睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰時我都以為係智慧齒<br />\n同你一樣生係最入嘅角位<br />\n飲水都痛到仆街<br />\n快啲睇，我知係好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\ni know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43473e5cbed42c69051cd504d65eb19cfcfb70e7","tid":387540,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:20:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我試過，好相似<br />\n去睇普通診所<br />\n醫生話係口腔潰瘍（嚴重版飛滋）<br />\n食幾日藥同用漱口水就康復</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲搞到我以為出智慧齒搞到頂住<br />\n聽日去睇睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就真係生智障齒開始痛痛地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前洗牙醫生話岀咗四分一隻，未使搞住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07e842d3469ee592a51df9988afc1513aff5ea6","tid":387540,"uid":6270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:26:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我試過，好相似<br />\n去睇普通診所<br />\n醫生話係口腔潰瘍（嚴重版飛滋）<br />\n食幾日藥同用漱口水就康復</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲搞到我以為出智慧齒搞到頂住<br />\n聽日去睇睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就真係生智障齒開始痛痛地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前洗牙醫生話岀咗四分一隻，未使搞住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但通常你去到睇牙醫十個有九個都會叫你剝左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}